re often sufficient\n% [YOUR_ADDRESS] \\\\ % Uncomment if needed\n% [YOUR_CITY_STATE_ZIP] \\\\ % Uncomment if needed\n+1-3155757385 \\\\ % <<< Placeholder\n\\href{mailto:bchikara@syr.edu}{\\nolinkurl{bchikara@syr.edu}} \\\\ % <<< Placeholder\n\\href{https://www.linkedin.com/in/bchikara/}{\\nolinkurl{linkedin.com/in/bchikara/}} \\\\ % <<< Placeholder\n\\href{}{\\nolinkurl{}} % <<< Placeholder\n\\vspace{2\\baselineskip} % Add space before date\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Date ---\n\\begin{raggedright}\n\\today \\\\ % Automatically inserts the current date\n\\vspace{2\\baselineskip} % Add space before recipient info\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Recipient Information ---\n% Placeholders will be replaced by tailor.py with escaped content\n\\begin{raggedright}\nHiring Team\n\nUpstart\n[Company Address]\nUnited States (Remote)\n\\vspace{2\\baselineskip} % Add space before salutation\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Salutation ---\n% Placeholder will be replaced by tailor.py with escaped content\n\\begin{raggedright}\nDear Dear Hiring Team, \\\\\n\\vspace{1\\baselineskip} % Add space before body\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Body Paragraph 1: Introduction ---\n% <<< Use unique, static placeholder >>>\n\\begin{raggedright}\nI am writing to express my enthusiastic interest in the Software Engineer, Consumer Platform with verification position at Upstart, as advertised on LinkedIn.  Upstart's mission of expanding access to affordable credit through AI-driven lending deeply resonates with me, and the opportunity to contribute to such an innovative and impactful company is incredibly exciting. My extensive experience in full-stack development, particularly with React and backend technologies like Ruby and Kotlin, aligns perfectly with the technical requirements outlined in the job description.\n\\vspace{1\\baselineskip}\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Body Paragraph 2: Qualifications Match ---\n% <<< Use unique, static placeholder >>>\n\\begin{raggedright}\nMy background encompasses a proven track record of success in designing and implementing scalable, resilient services.  At Deloitte, I consistently received the Applause Award for my contributions as a Senior Software Engineer, including leading teams, owning projects, and solving complex dashboard algorithms using React and Next.js---skills directly applicable to building and maintaining Upstart's consumer platform.  Furthermore, my experience at ToTheNew Pvt. Ltd. developing front-end solutions, including a COVID-19 dashboard and e-commerce platforms using Angular, demonstrates my ability to create maintainable solutions across various technologies.  My consistent problem-solving skills, honed through six months of consecutive LeetCode problem-solving, further solidify my ability to tackle complex challenges within Upstart's dynamic environment.\n\\vspace{1\\baselineskip}\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Body Paragraph 3: Why This Company/Role ---\n% <<< Use unique, static placeholder >>>\n\\begin{raggedright}\nI am particularly drawn to Upstart's commitment to leveraging AI to improve access to credit and its focus on creating a seamless and personalized consumer experience.  The opportunity to work on a core product platform, collaborating with cross-functional teams to build impactful solutions, strongly aligns with my career aspirations. I am confident that my skills and experience would make me a valuable asset to your team, and I am eager to discuss how I can contribute to Upstart's continued success. Thank you for your time and consideration.\n\\vspace{1\\baselineskip}\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Closing Paragraph ---\n% Placeholder will be replaced by tailor.py with escaped content\n\\begin{raggedright}\nThank you for considering my application. I have attached my resume for your review and welcome the opportunity to discuss how my skills and experience can benefit Upstart in an interview.\n\\vspace{2\\baselineskip} % Add space before closing\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n% --- Closing ---\n\\begin{raggedright}\nSincerely, \\\\\n\\vspace{3\\baselineskip} % Leave space for signature (optional for digital)\nBhupesh Chikara % <<< Placeholder for your name\n\\end{raggedright}\n\n\\end{document}\n", 'tailored_resume_text': '%-------------------------\n% Resume in Latex\n% Author : Jake Gutierrez / Modifications for Job Agent\n% Based off of: https://github.com/sb2nov/resume\n% License : MIT\n%------------------------\n\n\\documentclass[letterpaper,11pt]{article}\n\n\\usepackage{latexsym}\n\\usepackage[empty]{fullpage}\n\\usepackage{titlesec}\n\\usepackage{marvosym}\n\\usepackage[usenames,dvipsnames]{color}\n\\usepackage{verbatim}\n\\usepackage{enumitem}\n\\usepackage[hidelinks]{hyperref} % Keep hidelinks if you prefer no boxes around links\n\\usepackage{fancyhdr}\n\\usepackage[english]{babel}\n\\usepackage{tabularx}\n\\usepackage{xurl} % <<< For better line breaking\n% \\usepackage{fontawesome5} % Uncomment if you want to use icons in the header\n\\input{glyphtounicode}\n\n%----------FONT OPTIONS----------\n% sans-serif\n% \\usepackage[sfdefault]{FiraSans}\n% \\usepackage[sfdefault]{roboto}\n% \\usepackage[sfdefault]{noto-sans}\n% \\usepackage[default]{sourcesanspro} % A good, clean sans-serif option\n\n% serif\n% \\usepackage{CormorantGaramond}\n% \\usepackage{charter} % A good serif option\n\n\n\\pagestyle{fancy}\n\\fancyhf{} % clear all header and footer fields\n\\fancyfoot{}\n\\renewcommand{\\headrulewidth}{0pt}\n\\renewcommand{\\footrulewidth}{0pt}\n\n% Adjust margins\n\\addtolength{\\oddsidemargin}{-0.5in}\n\\addtolength{\\evensidemargin}{-0.5in}\n\\addtolength{\\textwidth}{1in}\n\\addtolength{\\topmargin}{-.5in}\n\\addtolength{\\textheight}{1.0in}\n\n% Set URL style - \\urlstyle{same} uses the current text font\n\\urlstyle{same}\n\n\\raggedbottom\n\\raggedright\n\\setlength{\\tabcolsep}{0in}\n\n% Sections formatting\n\\titleformat{\\section}{\n  \\vspace{-4pt}\\scshape\\raggedright\\large\n}{}{0em}{}[\\color{black}\\titlerule \\vspace{-5pt}]\n\n% Ensur